1
00:00:11,281 --> 00:00:15,517
<i>Hey boys, listen up!</i>

2
00:00:15,540 --> 00:00:20,281
<i>Humans aren't such a big deal</i>

3
00:00:20,991 --> 00:00:25,121
<i>Who needs tomorrow anyway,</i>

4
00:00:25,195 --> 00:00:28,392
<i>so don't hide your fists</i>

5
00:00:30,334 --> 00:00:32,598
<i>You're not old enough</i>

6
00:00:32,669 --> 00:00:38,972
<i>to sell your dreams away to uncertainty</i>

7
00:00:39,910 --> 00:00:44,347
<i>Hey boys, you're the only ones</i>

8
00:00:44,414 --> 00:00:47,941
<i>who can pull the trigger in your heart</i>

9
00:00:49,386 --> 00:00:51,320
<i>All the kids said</i>

10
00:00:51,388 --> 00:00:54,323
<i>We're living in this senseless, ridiculous,</i>

11
00:00:54,391 --> 00:00:58,691
<i>awesome world right at this moment,</i>

12
00:00:58,896 --> 00:01:01,160
<i>All the kids said</i>

13
00:01:01,231 --> 00:01:07,033
<i>Don't forget every truth or lie</i>

14
00:01:08,438 --> 00:01:10,774
<i>All the kids said</i>

15
00:01:10,774 --> 00:01:13,106
<i>We're way too young to die</i>

16
00:01:13,177 --> 00:01:17,978
<i>In this empty town lined with empty faces</i>

17
00:01:18,048 --> 00:01:20,243
<i>All the kids took off</i>

18
00:01:20,317 --> 00:01:22,785
<i>into this windless night</i>

19
00:01:22,853 --> 00:01:26,220
<i>Because they want to change something</i>

20
00:01:31,272 --> 00:01:36,300
<i>The End of Tears</i>

21
00:01:51,426 --> 00:01:53,053
By special...

22
00:01:54,128 --> 00:01:58,394
By special,
you meant that?!

23
00:02:03,438 --> 00:02:05,406
I don't feel like I'm gonna lose.

24
00:03:39,167 --> 00:03:41,931
Sasuke... you...

25
00:03:52,780 --> 00:03:55,578
<i>If they continue to be released</i>
<i>for a long period of time,</i>

26
00:03:55,650 --> 00:03:58,551
<i>Curse Marks will progressively</i>
<i>eat your body.</i>

27
00:03:58,619 --> 00:04:01,179
<i>When they have entirely</i>
<i>eaten you...</i>

28
00:04:01,255 --> 00:04:05,123
<i>you will lose yourself...forever.</i>

29
00:04:08,830 --> 00:04:10,297
<i>This body...</i>

30
00:04:11,199 --> 00:04:14,168
<i>It looks like there's no time to waste.</i>

31
00:04:23,444 --> 00:04:26,572
<i>I don't have any feeling</i>
<i>in my left arm...</i>

32
00:04:29,817 --> 00:04:31,876
That power you have...

33
00:04:33,921 --> 00:04:37,516
seems to involve
some risks too, huh?

34
00:04:41,696 --> 00:04:43,027
Did you know?

35
00:04:49,270 --> 00:04:50,498
That this place...

36
00:04:51,172 --> 00:04:53,766
is called the Final Valley.

37
00:04:56,411 --> 00:05:02,372
I think this is the perfect stage,
don't you think... Naruto?

38
00:05:12,160 --> 00:05:13,821
Oh yeah...

39
00:05:15,096 --> 00:05:17,963
I said there'd be
no more talking, didn't I?

40
00:05:19,333 --> 00:05:22,302
Well, in that case,
how about we bring it to a close...?

41
00:05:22,703 --> 00:05:24,603
This battle.

42
00:05:26,074 --> 00:05:28,133
All our battles up to now!

43
00:05:29,043 --> 00:05:32,672
Next for Squad Seven.
Naruto Uzumaki!

44
00:05:33,848 --> 00:05:35,110
Sakura Haruno!

45
00:05:36,717 --> 00:05:38,150
Yipeee!

46
00:05:38,219 --> 00:05:40,050
<i>With Naruto...?</i>

47
00:05:40,488 --> 00:05:42,319
And Sasuke Uchiha.

48
00:05:42,523 --> 00:05:43,990
Yipeee!

49
00:05:44,325 --> 00:05:46,088
<i>With Sasuke...?</i>

50
00:05:46,994 --> 00:05:50,157
Try not to slow me down, loser.

51
00:05:50,531 --> 00:05:52,556
You...!

52
00:05:52,633 --> 00:05:56,501
But... but... but... you told us...

53
00:05:56,637 --> 00:05:58,104
That's why they...

54
00:05:58,606 --> 00:06:01,200
Aren't we a three-man squad?

55
00:06:02,376 --> 00:06:06,039
That's right! We three are one!

56
00:06:06,380 --> 00:06:07,278
Hey!

57
00:06:09,083 --> 00:06:13,349
Are you hurt?
Scaredy Cat?

58
00:06:15,523 --> 00:06:22,019
Hey... are you hurt?
Scaredy Cat?

59
00:06:23,364 --> 00:06:26,026
You are one of the ones
I want to fight.

60
00:06:28,469 --> 00:06:29,868
Sasuke!

61
00:06:31,072 --> 00:06:35,441
I want... to fight you, too.

62
00:06:36,310 --> 00:06:39,507
I don't want to see
any more deaths

63
00:06:39,580 --> 00:06:43,448
of my precious comrades.

64
00:06:43,951 --> 00:06:45,418
Summoning Jutsu!

65
00:06:51,159 --> 00:06:55,391
I... will protect Sakura!

66
00:06:55,930 --> 00:06:57,420
What's so funny?

67
00:06:57,498 --> 00:07:00,661
Nothing's funny, believe it!
I'm happy!

68
00:07:01,569 --> 00:07:05,335
When I think I can finally
beat you here!

69
00:07:05,673 --> 00:07:09,165
What did you say?!
Don't talk foolish, you failure!

70
00:07:09,744 --> 00:07:13,009
I'm not going to be
a failure forever!

71
00:07:13,347 --> 00:07:14,974
Just bring it, now!

72
00:07:15,049 --> 00:07:18,075
Put on your headband before that!
I'll wait.

73
00:07:18,286 --> 00:07:20,345
I don't need such a thing...

74
00:07:20,688 --> 00:07:22,053
Just do it!

75
00:07:24,325 --> 00:07:29,695
You wouldn't even be able
to put one wound on my forehead!

76
00:07:29,931 --> 00:07:31,125
You're wrong!

77
00:07:31,199 --> 00:07:33,360
I'm saying this is a testament

78
00:07:33,434 --> 00:07:35,868
to fighting on equal terms
as a Leaf Shinobi!

79
00:07:36,304 --> 00:07:37,532
Naruto!

80
00:07:38,206 --> 00:07:39,673
Sasuke!

81
00:07:39,840 --> 00:07:41,774
I'll win no matter what!

82
00:07:41,842 --> 00:07:43,867
Don't flatter yourself!

83
00:07:44,412 --> 00:07:46,607
Stop it!

84
00:07:50,585 --> 00:07:52,746
And from this time onward...

85
00:08:04,899 --> 00:08:06,662
<i>Chidori!</i>

86
00:08:17,578 --> 00:08:19,102
<i>Rasengan!</i>

87
00:08:47,475 --> 00:08:49,033
- <i>Rasengan!</i>
- <i>Chidori!</i>

88
00:09:11,599 --> 00:09:13,396
- <i>Chidori!</i>
- <i>Rasengan!</i>

89
00:09:42,596 --> 00:09:44,029
<i>This Chakra...</i>

90
00:09:45,433 --> 00:09:46,491
<i>isn't good!</i>

91
00:13:04,698 --> 00:13:06,165
Naruto...

92
00:13:18,946 --> 00:13:20,277
I...

93
00:14:24,345 --> 00:14:27,314
It's started to rain!
Will it erase the scent?

94
00:14:28,182 --> 00:14:29,308
No problem.

95
00:14:29,984 --> 00:14:31,815
We're already close.
This way.

96
00:14:44,431 --> 00:14:45,864
<i>Was I too late...?</i>

97
00:14:54,341 --> 00:14:55,831
Naruto!

98
00:15:00,681 --> 00:15:02,842
Why did things come to this?!

99
00:15:13,494 --> 00:15:15,121
This is Sasuke's...

100
00:15:53,701 --> 00:15:58,331
I didn't make it in time...
please forgive me.

101
00:16:04,645 --> 00:16:05,805
Naruto...

102
00:16:07,514 --> 00:16:09,209
I know the kind of person you are...

103
00:16:10,284 --> 00:16:11,876
You must have made
a desperate effort.

104
00:16:18,592 --> 00:16:19,957
<i>Sasuke...</i>

105
00:16:43,584 --> 00:16:46,018
<i>That's my boy...</i>

106
00:16:58,866 --> 00:17:02,859
<i>With me, you're all</i>
<i>your father talks about...</i>

107
00:17:03,270 --> 00:17:05,500
<i>You are my one and only brother.</i>

108
00:17:06,206 --> 00:17:08,367
<i>I will continue to be for you...</i>

109
00:17:08,442 --> 00:17:11,172
<i>a wall that you must find</i>
<i>a way to cross over.</i>

110
00:17:12,780 --> 00:17:14,611
<i>Even if you were to hate me...</i>

111
00:17:17,584 --> 00:17:18,949
<i>You are someone</i>

112
00:17:19,019 --> 00:17:22,455
<i>who can obtain Mangekyo Sharingan</i>
<i>just like me...</i>

113
00:17:25,692 --> 00:17:28,320
<i>However, on one condition.</i>

114
00:17:34,434 --> 00:17:36,959
<i>Your closest friend...</i>

115
00:17:49,383 --> 00:17:50,850
The Final Valley...

116
00:17:51,451 --> 00:17:54,614
To think that Sasuke and Naruto
would battle it out here...

117
00:17:58,458 --> 00:18:00,392
How ironic...

118
00:18:03,130 --> 00:18:04,154
Yeah...

119
00:18:07,334 --> 00:18:09,063
When I look at
the flow of this water,

120
00:18:09,870 --> 00:18:16,400
it's as if I'm being confronted
by an eternal, never ending battle...

121
00:18:20,614 --> 00:18:22,878
Just like the fate of the two people
depicted in these statues here

122
00:18:22,950 --> 00:18:26,044
who founded the Village Hidden
in the Leaves...

123
00:18:30,791 --> 00:18:37,390
Naruto and Sasuke,
as long as you both live...

124
00:18:56,049 --> 00:18:58,643
<i>You have to kill...</i>

125
00:19:01,154 --> 00:19:03,145
<i>your closest friend!</i>

126
00:19:17,938 --> 00:19:19,405
<i>I'm not gonna...</i>

127
00:19:20,774 --> 00:19:23,402
<i>abide by everything you say!</i>

128
00:19:31,018 --> 00:19:34,579
<i>I will get my hands on power</i>
<i>doing it my own way!</i>

129
00:19:35,889 --> 00:19:39,791
<i>I will surpass you</i>
<i>doing it my own way!</i>

130
00:19:40,894 --> 00:19:42,384
<i>Without fail!</i>

131
00:19:56,310 --> 00:19:59,473
The rain's... let up, hasn't it?

132
00:20:00,714 --> 00:20:01,806
Yeah.

133
00:20:17,831 --> 00:20:19,594
With that much rain,

134
00:20:19,666 --> 00:20:21,793
I won't be able to pursue
the scent anymore.

135
00:20:23,103 --> 00:20:26,231
Naruto is more important now
than pursuing Sasuke.

136
00:20:28,075 --> 00:20:29,167
Yeah.

137
00:20:53,734 --> 00:20:56,703
It's gotten interesting, hasn't it?

138
00:20:58,338 --> 00:20:59,305
Yeah...

139
00:21:11,918 --> 00:21:16,582
<i>When I recalled the parts one by one,</i>

140
00:21:16,656 --> 00:21:22,959
<i>I felt as though</i>
<i>I had understood everything</i>

141
00:21:23,030 --> 00:21:33,531
<i>Faded words which I kept so close to me</i>

142
00:21:33,840 --> 00:21:43,306
<i>Speechless nights, a hint of warmth,</i>

143
00:21:45,052 --> 00:21:50,046
<i>and this distant yearning for you</i>

144
00:21:50,357 --> 00:21:59,356
<i>I live, simply repeating this cycle</i>

145
00:22:01,535 --> 00:22:11,069
<i>Held in my two hands</i>
<i>A droplet of time</i>

146
00:22:12,512 --> 00:22:21,511
<i>Softly clutching forgotten memories</i>
<i>Lost words</i>

147
00:22:30,664 --> 00:22:34,259
<i>I'll keep these thoughts...</i>

148
00:22:37,537 --> 00:22:42,167
I'm sorry.
I'm really sorry, Sakura.

149
00:22:42,843 --> 00:22:48,145
I made a once in a lifetime promise
that I would bring Sasuke back.

150
00:22:49,316 --> 00:22:51,978
But, I'm not finished yet!

151
00:22:52,152 --> 00:22:54,086
I'll fulfill my promise,
no matter what!

152
00:22:54,254 --> 00:22:56,313
Since that was what
I was always saying...

153
00:22:56,389 --> 00:22:58,084
that I won't go back on my word.

154
00:22:58,158 --> 00:23:01,218
That's my Way of Ninja!

155
00:23:01,828 --> 00:23:04,296
Next episode:
"The Promise That Could Not Be Kept"
